    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>Red hat 5</h1>

<h2>Server Setup</h2>

<p>$ sudo vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config</p>

<p>make sure X11Forwarding is turned on:</p>

<pre><code>X11Forwarding yes
</code></pre>

<p>Then restart ssh service:</p>

<p>$ sudo /etc/init.d/sshd restart</p>

<h2>Client</h2>

<p>$ ssh -X <a href="&#109;&#x61;&#105;&#x6c;&#x74;&#111;&#x3a;&#103;&#99;&#112;&#x40;&#x31;&#x30;&#46;&#x30;&#46;&#50;&#46;&#52;&#56;">&#103;&#99;&#112;&#64;&#x31;&#x30;&#46;&#x30;&#46;&#x32;&#x2e;&#x34;&#56;</a></p>

<p>$ gedit &amp;</p>

<p>Bingo!</p>

<p>Ref: <a href="http://www.cyberciti.biz/tips/running-x-window-graphical-application-over-ssh-session.html">http://www.cyberciti.biz/tips/running-x-window-graphical-application-over-ssh-session.html</a></p>
